{
  "video_id": "0g0S34XE2b8",
  "title": "How we can bring mental health support to refugees | Essam Daod",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13437.0,
      "end_time": 15817.0,
      "text": "For the last two and a half years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15841.0,
      "end_time": 19262.0,
      "text": "I'm one of the few, if not the only, child psychiatrist"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19286.0,
      "end_time": 22791.0,
      "text": "operating in refugee camps, shorelines and rescue boats"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22815.0,
      "end_time": 24974.0,
      "text": "in Greece and the Mediterranean Sea."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25410.0,
      "end_time": 27649.0,
      "text": "And I can say, with great confidence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27673.0,
      "end_time": 31125.0,
      "text": "that we are witnessing a mental-health catastrophe"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31149.0,
      "end_time": 34712.0,
      "text": "that will affect most of us, and it will change our world."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35784.0,
      "end_time": 39772.0,
      "text": "I live in Haifa, but nowadays, I spend most of my time abroad."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40204.0,
      "end_time": 43180.0,
      "text": "During my time on the Greek island of Lesbos"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43204.0,
      "end_time": 45593.0,
      "text": "and on the rescue boats in the Mediterranean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45617.0,
      "end_time": 48672.0,
      "text": "thousands of refugee boats arrived to the shoreline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48696.0,
      "end_time": 52149.0,
      "text": "crowded with more than 1.5 million refugees."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52173.0,
      "end_time": 54235.0,
      "text": "One-fourth of them are children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54259.0,
      "end_time": 55859.0,
      "text": "fleeing war and hardship."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56331.0,
      "end_time": 59799.0,
      "text": "Each boat carries different sufferings and traumas"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59823.0,
      "end_time": 63597.0,
      "text": "from Syria, Iraq, Afganistan and different countries in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64116.0,
      "end_time": 65952.0,
      "text": "In the last three years alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65976.0,
      "end_time": 69355.0,
      "text": "more than 12,000 refugees lost their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69379.0,
      "end_time": 73212.0,
      "text": "And hundreds of thousands lost their souls and their mental health"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73236.0,
      "end_time": 75839.0,
      "text": "due to this cruel and traumatic experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77203.0,
      "end_time": 79204.0,
      "text": "I want to tell you about Omar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79522.0,
      "end_time": 81545.0,
      "text": "a five-year-old Syrian refugee boy"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 81569.0,
      "end_time": 84911.0,
      "text": "who arrived to the shore on Lesbos on a crowded rubber boat."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 86204.0,
      "end_time": 89592.0,
      "text": "Crying, frightened, unable to understand what's happening to him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89617.0,
      "end_time": 92728.0,
      "text": "he was right on the verge of developing a new trauma."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93770.0,
      "end_time": 95926.0,
      "text": "I knew right away that this was a golden hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95950.0,
      "end_time": 99482.0,
      "text": "a short period of time in which I could change his story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 99506.0,
      "end_time": 101600.0,
      "text": "I could change the story"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 101300.0,
      "end_time": 103934.0,
      "text": "that he would tell himself for the rest of his life."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 103958.0,
      "end_time": 107601.0,
      "text": "I could reframe his memories."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 107990.0,
      "end_time": 112487.0,
      "text": "I quickly held out my hands and said to his shaking mother in Arabic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 112527.0,
      "end_time": 114467.0,
      "text": "(Arabic) \"Ateeni elwalad o khudi nafas.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 114507.0,
      "end_time": 116351.0,
      "text": "\"Give me the boy, and take a breath.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 116887.0,
      "end_time": 118620.0,
      "text": "His mother gave him to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 119490.0,
      "end_time": 123664.0,
      "text": "Omar looked at me with scared, tearful eyes and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 123688.0,
      "end_time": 126536.0,
      "text": "(Arabic) \"Ammo (uncle in Arabic), shu hada?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 126560.0,
      "end_time": 127737.0,
      "text": "\"What is this?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 127761.0,
      "end_time": 131250.0,
      "text": "as he pointed out to the police helicopter hovering above us."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132610.0,
      "end_time": 133442.0,
      "text": "\"It's a helicopter!"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 133466.0,
      "end_time": 135832.0,
      "text": "It's here to photograph you with big cameras,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135856.0,
      "end_time": 138667.0,
      "text": "because only the great and the powerful heroes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 138691.0,
      "end_time": 140920.0,
      "text": "like you, Omar, can cross the sea.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142413.0,
      "end_time": 147270.0,
      "text": "Omar looked at me, stopped crying and asked me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147657.0,
      "end_time": 148827.0,
      "text": "(Arabic) \"Ana batal?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 148872.0,
      "end_time": 151131.0,
      "text": "\"I'm a hero?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152610.0,
      "end_time": 154553.0,
      "text": "I talked to Omar for 15 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154577.0,
      "end_time": 157276.0,
      "text": "And I gave his parents some guidance to follow."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 157300.0,
      "end_time": 159205.0,
      "text": "This short psychological intervention"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159229.0,
      "end_time": 162641.0,
      "text": "decreases the prevalence of post-traumatic stress disorder"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162665.0,
      "end_time": 165149.0,
      "text": "and other mental health issues in the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165173.0,
      "end_time": 167601.0,
      "text": "preparing Omar to get an education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167625.0,
      "end_time": 170664.0,
      "text": "join the workforce, raise a family and beyond."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170688.0,
      "end_time": 171841.0,
      "text": "How?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 171866.0,
      "end_time": 175122.0,
      "text": "By stimulating the good memories that will be stored in the amygdala,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 175146.0,
      "end_time": 177266.0,
      "text": "the emotional storage of the human brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 177290.0,
      "end_time": 179418.0,
      "text": "These memories will fight the traumatic ones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 179442.0,
      "end_time": 181976.0,
      "text": "if they are reactivated in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 182532.0,
      "end_time": 185295.0,
      "text": "To Omar, the smell of the sea will not just remind him"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 185319.0,
      "end_time": 187476.0,
      "text": "of his traumatic journey from Syria."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 187501.0,
      "end_time": 191818.0,
      "text": "Because to Omar, this story is now a story of bravery."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 192450.0,
      "end_time": 194593.0,
      "text": "This is the power of the golden hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 194617.0,
      "end_time": 198236.0,
      "text": "which can reframe the trauma and establish a new narrative."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 199442.0,
      "end_time": 205650.0,
      "text": "But Omar is only one out of more than 350,000 children"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 205674.0,
      "end_time": 209705.0,
      "text": "without the proper mental health support in this crisis alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 210284.0,
      "end_time": 213966.0,
      "text": "Three hundred and fifty thousand children and me."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 218609.0,
      "text": "We need mental health professionals"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 218634.0,
      "end_time": 222340.0,
      "text": "to join rescue teams during times of active crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 222563.0,
      "end_time": 227226.0,
      "text": "This is why my wife and I and friends co-founded \"Humanity Crew.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 228193.0,
      "end_time": 230321.0,
      "text": "One of the few aid organizations in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 230345.0,
      "end_time": 232964.0,
      "text": "that specializes in providing psychosocial aid"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 232988.0,
      "end_time": 235569.0,
      "text": "and first-response mental health interventions"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235593.0,
      "end_time": 238227.0,
      "text": "to refugees and displaced populations."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 238252.0,
      "end_time": 241600.0,
      "text": "To provide them with a suitable intervention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 241300.0,
      "end_time": 244458.0,
      "text": "we create the four-step approach, a psychosocial work plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 244482.0,
      "end_time": 247918.0,
      "text": "that follows the refugees on each step of their journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 248371.0,
      "end_time": 252601.0,
      "text": "Starting inside the sea, on the rescue boats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 252625.0,
      "end_time": 254720.0,
      "text": "as mental health lifeguards."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 254744.0,
      "end_time": 259514.0,
      "text": "Later in the camps, hospitals and through our online clinic"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 259538.0,
      "end_time": 262434.0,
      "text": "that breaks down borders and overcomes languages."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 262792.0,
      "end_time": 266370.0,
      "text": "And ending in the asylum countries, helping them integrate."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 266514.0,
      "end_time": 269442.0,
      "text": "Since our first mission in 2015,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 269466.0,
      "end_time": 272283.0,
      "text": "\"Humanity Crew\" had 194 delegations"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 272307.0,
      "end_time": 274847.0,
      "text": "of qualified, trained volunteers and therapists."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 275275.0,
      "end_time": 279433.0,
      "text": "We have provided 26,000 hours of mental health support"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 279458.0,
      "end_time": 281347.0,
      "text": "to over 10,000 refugees."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 282600.0,
      "end_time": 286815.0,
      "text": "We can all do something to prevent this mental health catastrophe."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 287387.0,
      "end_time": 292280.0,
      "text": "We need to acknowledge that first aid is not just needed for the body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 292520.0,
      "end_time": 295171.0,
      "text": "but it has also to include the mind, the soul."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 295195.0,
      "end_time": 297703.0,
      "text": "The impact on the soul is hardly visible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 297727.0,
      "end_time": 300193.0,
      "text": "but the damage can be there for life."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 300680.0,
      "end_time": 305650.0,
      "text": "Let's not forget that what distinguishes us humans from machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 305890.0,
      "end_time": 308866.0,
      "text": "is the beautiful and the delicate soul within us."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 310610.0,
      "end_time": 313258.0,
      "text": "Let's try harder to save more Omars."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 313720.0,
      "end_time": 314881.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 314905.0,
      "end_time": 318227.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 318251.0,
      "end_time": 320340.0,
      "text": "(Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 320364.0,
      "end_time": 322857.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}